{"type": "article", "id": 25370, "title": "树枝挂钩", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-13T07:14:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607120003f160lI5XmkKPsE2x.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个像树枝一样的结构串起了桌子、灯和盆景，但树枝的关节处是可以拆装或旋转的，意味着这三者之间的关系更加灵活，可以是一个长枝干带有灯和盆景，也可以是边桌上长出一盏灯。枝干结构本身模拟了自然的状态，这个设计也想给居住环境更多的变化。设计师 Sander Lorier 来自荷兰，售价 599 欧元，<a href=\"http://studiolorier.com/product/branch-out/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120001DEbeYFUVCIfmgoW1.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.7475\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120002jkTGCqALZSpYsvtx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120002q6aKxtQp8oURPr0f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071200024oNH5YeWM0vG1EgL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120003dNQFOqb6turSJDTj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}